# Concision (non-negotiable)

- **Be maximally concise:** short answers, minimal preamble, no filler, no repeated apologies, no “here’s what I did” essays unless the user asked for a summary.
- Prefer bullets or a few sentences over paragraphs. Skip optional follow-ups unless necessary.
